data.title: McIntire Investors' Report 22
data.meta_description: McIntire donors support our mission, sustain our excellence, and strengthen our future. We are immensely grateful for the generous contributions made between July 1, 2022 and June 30, 2023.
data.text:
When it comes to the generosity of our donors, the opportunities that your gifts have created for the Commerce School and our students are extraordinary.

Thanks to you—our dedicated community—this past academic year is proof of the amazing things we are capable of accomplishing together.

Nicole Thorne Jenkins

John A. Griffin Dean
